China May Invest 10 Tln Yuan in Renewable Energy, Shanghai Securities Says

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-04-28T06:13:19Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-28/china-may-invest-10-tln-yuan-in-renewable-energy-shanghai-securities-says.html
China  may invest more than 10
trillion yuan for the development of renewable energy over 15
years to meet its target of reducing 40 percent to 45 percent of
CO2 emissions, the Shanghai Securities News reported today,
citing an unidentified official at the National Climate Change
Expert Committee.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bloomberg News at 
 swong139@bloomberg.net  